Notes:
[1] These archives represent the messages sent to CLASSICS-L prior to the beginning of the locally threaded archives (12 July 1998).
[2] These messages are available to anyone who sends the proper commands to listproc@u.washington.edu. The list archives thus requested arrive in bundles of messages. These bundles have been split into individual HTML pages by a locally written Perl script.
[3] There are some glitches in the archives as they are represented here, but these ought to be mainly cosmetic. All of the data is supposed to be available.
